                        </td>
                        <td class="text-center border2">
                            &nbsp;
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="10%">&nbsp;</td>
                        <td colspan="4" class="text-center font-size-9" width="100%">договор, заказ-наряд</td>
                        <td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left: 1px solid #000000;" align="right">дата&nbsp;</td>
                        <td class="text-center border2">
                            &nbsp;
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="10%">&nbsp;</td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="30%">&nbsp;</td>
                        <td style="font-size: 9px; border-left: 1px solid #000000; border-right: 1px solid #000000; border-top: 1px solid #000000;"
                            align="center" width="5%" nowrap>номер документа
                        </td>
                        <td style="font-size: 9px; border-right: 1px solid #000000; border-top: 1px solid #000000;"
                            align="center" width="5%" nowrap>дата составления
                        </td>
                        <td colspan="2" align="right">Транспортная накладная&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
                        <td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; border-left: 1px solid #000000;" align="right"
                            width="5%">номер&nbsp;
                        </td>
                        <td class="text-center border2"
                            width="5%">&nbsp;
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="font-size-13" valign="bottom" colspan="2" align="right"><strong>ТОВАРНАЯ
